{"tid":497784,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯儲局加息在即 一個月港元拆息升至1.08厘","createTime":"2017-12-13T06:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T07:07:06.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0328822a59bc116abfd8d5c0a63f0d67617a98ba","tid":497784,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>美聯儲局加息在即 一個月港元拆息升至1.08厘</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國聯儲局宣布加息在即，加上受年結因素影響，本港銀行同業拆息（Hibor）全線上升。據財資市場公會資料顯示，與按揭息息相關的一個月拆息升0.01厘，至到1.08厘，創九年新高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171213_FI_Hong_Kong-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171213_FI_Hong_Kong-2.jpg&h=9cbe34c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔夜拆息亦0.08厘升至0.1厘之上，一星期及兩星期拆息分別升至0.23厘及0.39厘，較上日分別升0.03厘及0.05厘。三個月拆息升至1.26厘。長期方面，六個月及一年拆息分別報1.33厘及1.5厘。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯儲局本港時間周四凌晨公布議息結果，利率期貨數據顯示，市場預期肯定會加息四分之一厘，到1.25至1.5厘。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，據報指美國國會參眾兩院最快下星期表決協調版本的稅改方案，企業稅率最終會降至21%，並在聖誕節前交予總統特朗普簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2663257-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%8B%86%E6%81%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B31-08%E5%8E%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2663257-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%2581%25AF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258D%25B3-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258B%2586%25E6%2581%25AF%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2587%25B31-08%25E5%258E%2598&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2FwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=cb276367\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2663257-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%8B%86%E6%81%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B31-08%E5%8E%98</a>"},{"pid":"5a5eda1abf572ca34dc63ee773fa151bc4030156","tid":497784,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb06158d114bf3e9ec17737b9e4d6ddf92e02390","tid":497784,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"加得個小小息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}